    "body": "When **this plugin** and **group entry verification** are enabled, inviting a bot into the group will be recognized as a new member, **but sending verification information to the bot will not resolve the issue.\n\nI know there's a Chinese idiom, \"mutual destruction,\" which is very similar to this bug.\n\n**It is recommended to refer to the [Napcat documentation](https://napcat.apifox.cn/5430207m0) for repair instructions.**",
